WEBVTT

00:00:00.520 --> 00:00:05.680
All right, well, good evening, family.

00:00:02.960 --> 00:00:07.360
Thank you for joining us again tonight.

00:00:05.680 --> 00:00:09.520
We're going to pray. I have some things

00:00:07.360 --> 00:00:11.840
to share with you that I saw today when

00:00:09.520 --> 00:00:15.440
I was in my own prayer time,

00:00:11.840 --> 00:00:16.880
and some of it's kind of disturbing.

00:00:15.440 --> 00:00:19.200
But I'm just going to be

00:00:16.880 --> 00:00:23.040
bold in what I say

00:00:19.200 --> 00:00:25.840
and say exactly what I saw.

00:00:27.800 --> 00:00:32.200
I don't know—you can pray with

00:00:29.400 --> 00:00:33.800
it, you can pray over it.

00:00:33.800 --> 00:00:36.559
A

00:00:35.160 --> 00:00:37.720
lot of times when the Lord shows me

00:00:36.560 --> 00:00:39.160
these things, I don't know what I'm supposed to do

00:00:37.720 --> 00:00:41.560
other than keep interceding

00:00:39.160 --> 00:00:43.360
like I always do. But when you have a

00:00:41.560 --> 00:00:44.880
crowd that the Lord has blessed me with, and

00:00:43.360 --> 00:00:47.400
all y'all coming over here, you

00:00:44.880 --> 00:00:49.040
prayer warriors know how to pray

00:00:47.400 --> 00:00:51.600
and intercede for other

00:00:49.040 --> 00:00:54.160
nations. Now, I usually get

00:00:51.600 --> 00:00:56.600
assignments for America,

00:00:54.160 --> 00:00:58.440
and I pray for Trump all the time.

00:00:56.600 --> 00:01:00.200
I feel like my main

00:00:58.440 --> 00:01:03.440
mission has been praying

00:01:00.200 --> 00:01:06.280
over our nation for revival, for

00:01:03.440 --> 00:01:09.160
an awakening under God, and

00:01:06.280 --> 00:01:11.760
for America to have one last call—one

00:01:09.160 --> 00:01:14.039
last push for a harvest of souls bigger

00:01:11.760 --> 00:01:16.360
than what we've ever seen before.

00:01:14.040 --> 00:01:18.280
God's not done with America yet. I truly

00:01:16.360 --> 00:01:20.440
believe we're about to see the greatest

00:01:18.280 --> 00:01:23.280
harvest, the greatest demonstrations, and

00:01:20.440 --> 00:01:26.360
manifestations of the glory of God in

00:01:23.280 --> 00:01:29.560
our churches and our stadiums. I

00:01:26.360 --> 00:01:31.320
don't believe that we have room enough

00:01:29.560 --> 00:01:34.680
to receive all that we're about to

00:01:31.320 --> 00:01:37.759
receive as far as the outpouring and

00:01:34.680 --> 00:01:41.240
the souls. There are 340 million

00:01:37.760 --> 00:01:44.240
people in America—or 344—but

00:01:41.240 --> 00:01:46.039
I believe the Dallas Cowboys Stadium

00:01:44.240 --> 00:01:48.399
is not big enough.

00:01:46.040 --> 00:01:50.240
I believe it will be like Charlie Kirk's

00:01:48.400 --> 00:01:53.760
funeral, where they had to have the

00:01:50.240 --> 00:01:56.640
overflow of 77 or 80,000 people

00:01:53.760 --> 00:01:58.680
plus the overflow next door,

00:01:56.640 --> 00:02:00.520
because there was not enough room for

00:01:58.680 --> 00:02:01.880
just a funeral for his home-going

00:02:00.520 --> 00:02:05.840
service.

00:02:01.880 --> 00:02:08.639
I keep seeing a major

00:02:05.840 --> 00:02:11.240
move of God in America, a major move of

00:02:08.639 --> 00:02:14.279
God in Latino nations,

00:02:11.240 --> 00:02:17.240
and in Asia and Africa. There will be a

00:02:14.280 --> 00:02:19.840
Holy Ghost Woodstock with

00:02:17.240 --> 00:02:22.720
fields full of people because

00:02:19.840 --> 00:02:25.560
the coliseums and even the Texas

00:02:22.720 --> 00:02:27.760
Motor Speedway can't hold all the people

00:02:25.560 --> 00:02:31.080
for what's about to happen.

00:02:27.760 --> 00:02:34.160
I saw a Holy Ghost Woodstock

00:02:31.080 --> 00:02:36.600
with fields full of people as far

00:02:34.160 --> 00:02:38.680
as the eye could see, coming for healing

00:02:36.600 --> 00:02:41.079
and demonstrations and manifestations of

00:02:38.680 --> 00:02:42.880
the glory. It was the parking that was

00:02:41.080 --> 00:02:46.160
the problem;

00:02:42.880 --> 00:02:47.760
there was no place to put all the cars.

00:02:46.160 --> 00:02:50.280
Think about that.

00:02:47.760 --> 00:02:52.200
Have you ever been to a major event and

00:02:50.280 --> 00:02:54.640
you have to walk

00:02:52.200 --> 00:02:56.880
blocks away from the stadium

00:02:54.640 --> 00:02:58.320
because there's no place to

00:02:56.880 --> 00:03:00.040
park?

00:02:58.320 --> 00:03:02.320
And then you want to leave early because

00:03:00.040 --> 00:03:05.000
it's terrible to even get out for

00:03:02.320 --> 00:03:08.519
traffic because the traffic's so bad to

00:03:05.000 --> 00:03:08.519
leave.

00:03:08.840 --> 00:03:11.920
So, I think it's interesting whenever

00:03:11.920 --> 00:03:18.000
the Lord speaks to me like he did today

00:03:15.160 --> 00:03:19.560
concerning Colombia.

00:03:19.560 --> 00:03:25.200
I was shown to pray for the new

00:03:23.600 --> 00:03:27.760
president or prime minister—whoever

00:03:25.200 --> 00:03:30.399
this is with the beard—and

00:03:27.760 --> 00:03:31.640
the Lord had me interceding for this

00:03:30.400 --> 00:03:35.080
man

00:03:31.640 --> 00:03:37.679
because of the attacks that will come

00:03:35.080 --> 00:03:41.959
against his life as he comes against the

00:03:37.680 --> 00:03:45.640
cartel and the corruption in Colombia. I saw in

00:03:41.959 --> 00:03:47.680
great detail that the

00:03:45.640 --> 00:03:50.279
cartel

00:03:47.680 --> 00:03:50.280
was

00:03:50.600 --> 00:03:56.079
planning something. He has two friends—one

00:03:53.440 --> 00:03:57.640
with a beard

00:03:56.080 --> 00:03:59.280
and another man that looked

00:03:57.640 --> 00:04:01.640
younger—and

00:03:59.280 --> 00:04:04.000
the cartel severed their heads

00:04:01.640 --> 00:04:06.000
and sent them to him in a box as

00:04:04.000 --> 00:04:09.120
a warning.

00:04:06.000 --> 00:04:11.959
The Lord showed me

00:04:09.120 --> 00:04:14.280
major attempts on this man's

00:04:11.959 --> 00:04:16.959
life, and he's a conservative from what I

00:04:14.280 --> 00:04:20.399
understand. In prayer, I

00:04:16.959 --> 00:04:22.200
saw him

00:04:20.399 --> 00:04:24.320
giving praise and glory to Jesus for

00:04:22.200 --> 00:04:27.960
winning the election yesterday.

00:04:24.320 --> 00:04:30.480
But I saw major disruption as he tries

00:04:27.960 --> 00:04:32.719
to come against the cartel and

00:04:30.480 --> 00:04:35.600
corruption in his government. His

00:04:32.720 --> 00:04:39.160
life was in danger. They use an

00:04:35.600 --> 00:04:41.480
intimidation tactic in the days ahead

00:04:39.160 --> 00:04:43.400
to eliminate people that he knows,

00:04:41.480 --> 00:04:45.360
and they take their body

00:04:43.400 --> 00:04:47.359
parts and give them to him, trying

00:04:45.360 --> 00:04:49.480
to tell him, 'You do what we tell you to

00:04:47.360 --> 00:04:51.480
do, or you're next. Your family, your

00:04:49.480 --> 00:04:55.560
wife, your kids, whatever.'I saw

00:04:51.480 --> 00:04:58.800
boxes full of his friends;

00:04:55.560 --> 00:05:00.960
it was very dark.

00:04:58.800 --> 00:05:02.960
As I was

00:05:00.960 --> 00:05:06.520
interceding and praying, I

00:05:02.960 --> 00:05:09.479
could see a woman

00:05:06.520 --> 00:05:11.919
about

00:05:09.480 --> 00:05:14.320
30 years old,

00:05:11.919 --> 00:05:16.719
and she was a witch.

00:05:14.320 --> 00:05:21.159
The Lord let me see this woman—that

00:05:16.720 --> 00:05:24.080
she was able to transform into a dog

00:05:21.160 --> 00:05:26.720
and into bats.

00:05:24.080 --> 00:05:28.320
It was demonic; she would turn into like

00:05:26.720 --> 00:05:31.880
a werewolf.

00:05:28.320 --> 00:05:35.159
I could see her spying

00:05:31.880 --> 00:05:37.200
on this man and his cabinet

00:05:35.160 --> 00:05:40.680
meetings in the days ahead.

00:05:37.200 --> 00:05:42.800
She would know what was coming, like

00:05:40.680 --> 00:05:44.520
the prophets in the Bible who knew

00:05:42.800 --> 00:05:46.320
where the kings would be,

00:05:44.520 --> 00:05:48.120
and they would go back and tell

00:05:46.320 --> 00:05:49.719
the good king what was

00:05:48.120 --> 00:05:51.000
coming so they would be ahead of the

00:05:49.720 --> 00:05:53.120
plan.

00:05:51.000 --> 00:05:55.600
I saw his plan unfolding,

00:05:53.120 --> 00:05:57.360
trying to help the government, but

00:05:55.600 --> 00:06:00.000
they would be ahead of him because of

00:05:57.360 --> 00:06:03.120
the witch.

00:06:00.000 --> 00:06:06.360
They knew he was coming after the

00:06:03.120 --> 00:06:09.160
coke plants and the drug cartel.

00:06:11.320 --> 00:06:15.240
The witch would transform

00:06:13.040 --> 00:06:18.000
into a bat—it's

00:06:15.240 --> 00:06:20.840
demonic—and

00:06:18.000 --> 00:06:22.720
it would split into two.

00:06:20.840 --> 00:06:24.200
They would fly and she

00:06:22.720 --> 00:06:25.960
would be watching and

00:06:24.200 --> 00:06:27.360
able to listen, then

00:06:25.960 --> 00:06:29.840
go back and tell them

00:06:27.360 --> 00:06:32.919
where he was coming. But

00:06:29.840 --> 00:06:35.640
the Lord said, 'If you anoint the

00:06:32.919 --> 00:06:38.840
room and

00:06:35.640 --> 00:06:41.680
your family with oil,

00:06:38.840 --> 00:06:43.719
I will provide a hedge of protection

00:06:41.680 --> 00:06:46.520
so they won't

00:06:43.720 --> 00:06:49.560
hear what you're going to do.'I

00:06:46.520 --> 00:06:51.599
saw anointing oil

00:06:49.560 --> 00:06:53.680
dripping from the post and the Lord

00:06:51.600 --> 00:06:55.320
said this would be applied as faith,

00:06:53.680 --> 00:06:58.040
like his blood.

00:06:55.320 --> 00:07:01.000
The blood will shield you from the

00:06:58.040 --> 00:07:04.000
demonic coming against you, sir.

00:07:01.000 --> 00:07:05.520
I saw the blood of Jesus

00:07:04.000 --> 00:07:08.160
covering him,

00:07:05.520 --> 00:07:10.479
and I saw an angel go before him.

00:07:08.160 --> 00:07:13.440
He'll have great favor

00:07:10.480 --> 00:07:15.360
to bring great revival in Colombia in

00:07:13.440 --> 00:07:17.240
the days ahead.

00:07:15.360 --> 00:07:19.360
There'll be a major move of God in Colombia.

00:07:17.240 --> 00:07:22.600
For the Lord said, 'I want a

00:07:19.360 --> 00:07:24.720
great harvest of souls in Colombia.'A

00:07:22.600 --> 00:07:26.880
'shaking to awaken'will come to the

00:07:24.720 --> 00:07:28.240
people of Colombia, and

00:07:26.880 --> 00:07:30.560
there'll be

00:07:28.240 --> 00:07:33.200
witchcraft spirits that have never been

00:07:30.560 --> 00:07:35.960
tested before, but the glory of God will

00:07:33.200 --> 00:07:39.560
go into Colombia and shake that

00:07:35.960 --> 00:07:39.560
nation.

00:07:39.680 --> 00:07:44.080
He said,

00:07:42.360 --> 00:07:46.200
'Pray for this man, for I have put him

00:07:44.080 --> 00:07:47.919
there.'I

00:07:47.920 --> 00:07:52.000
saw

00:07:49.680 --> 00:07:54.600
a shaking in Brazil and across

00:07:52.000 --> 00:07:56.320
South America, and

00:07:54.600 --> 00:07:58.640
there'll be a great

00:07:56.320 --> 00:08:00.400
revival coming. A

00:07:58.640 --> 00:08:02.680
harvest of souls like we've never seen

00:08:00.400 --> 00:08:04.880
before will come into South America.

00:08:02.680 --> 00:08:06.840
The same will be with

00:08:04.880 --> 00:08:08.960
South Korea and a lot

00:08:06.840 --> 00:08:10.840
of nations.

00:08:08.960 --> 00:08:12.280
It was

00:08:10.840 --> 00:08:14.679
interesting

00:08:12.280 --> 00:08:16.679
as I was seeing

00:08:16.680 --> 00:08:22.280
into his office; I saw a lot of wood, and

00:08:18.480 --> 00:08:23.560
I saw this woman lurking in the shadows.

00:08:23.560 --> 00:08:27.680
It's about stopping drug

00:08:25.680 --> 00:08:29.640
trafficking, sex

00:08:27.680 --> 00:08:31.440
trafficking, and this

00:08:29.640 --> 00:08:34.319
demonic

00:08:31.440 --> 00:08:36.719
agenda to kill, steal, and destroy. God

00:08:34.320 --> 00:08:39.200
wants to raise up a generation of Holy

00:08:36.719 --> 00:08:41.039
Ghost and fire.

00:08:39.200 --> 00:08:43.000
But we've got to

00:08:41.039 --> 00:08:45.720
get out of the

00:08:43.000 --> 00:08:48.120
lukewarm seeker-friendly stuff.

00:08:45.720 --> 00:08:50.760
The enemy is ahead of us because

00:08:48.120 --> 00:08:53.280
we don't embrace the supernatural in

00:08:50.760 --> 00:08:56.040
the church; we push it away.

00:08:53.280 --> 00:08:58.240
We attack

00:08:56.040 --> 00:09:01.599
the laughing, the healing, and

00:08:58.240 --> 00:09:04.720
people getting set

00:09:01.600 --> 00:09:07.000
free from demonic spirits, saying,

00:09:04.720 --> 00:09:10.000
'That's not

00:09:07.000 --> 00:09:11.880
for today.'If Jesus cast out devils,

00:09:10.000 --> 00:09:14.760
we cast out devils.

00:09:11.880 --> 00:09:17.040
Go into all the world, lay hands on

00:09:14.760 --> 00:09:18.880
the sick, raise

00:09:17.040 --> 00:09:20.880
the dead, and do

00:09:18.880 --> 00:09:23.040
the Great Commission.

00:09:23.040 --> 00:09:28.360
But the church has gone limp-wristed.

00:09:26.000 --> 00:09:30.640
They have no backbone.

00:09:28.360 --> 00:09:33.320
We have let the enemy take ground

00:09:30.640 --> 00:09:36.240
that should be ours. Greater is he that

00:09:33.320 --> 00:09:38.880
is in us than he that is in the world.

00:09:36.240 --> 00:09:41.640
Jesus Christ paid the price for you to

00:09:38.880 --> 00:09:43.880
walk in victory over the devil. The

00:09:41.640 --> 00:09:46.040
Devil shouldn't be running over you.

00:09:43.880 --> 00:09:47.880
We should be running over him. Why?

00:09:46.040 --> 00:09:48.959
Because He defeated him once and for

00:09:47.880 --> 00:09:50.880
all.

00:09:48.960 --> 00:09:53.800
And we're wall-to-wall Holy Ghost.

00:09:50.880 --> 00:09:55.960
Christ in me, the hope of glory.

00:09:53.800 --> 00:09:57.560
And the church—the reason why we're

00:09:55.960 --> 00:09:59.640
not seeing results is because the preachers

00:09:57.560 --> 00:10:01.119
aren't preaching repentance, they're not

00:09:59.640 --> 00:10:03.240
preaching holiness, and they're not

00:10:01.120 --> 00:10:05.400
preaching the soon-coming of the Lord

00:10:03.240 --> 00:10:08.000
Jesus Christ.

00:10:05.400 --> 00:10:09.480
And tonight, I'm here to tell you Jesus

00:10:08.000 --> 00:10:11.880
is coming.

00:10:09.480 --> 00:10:14.200
And it's time to get off of our blessed

00:10:11.880 --> 00:10:16.800
assurance and get our heinies into

00:10:14.200 --> 00:10:20.080
motion and do what God's called us to do

00:10:16.800 --> 00:10:22.520
so we don't lose another generation.

00:10:20.080 --> 00:10:24.560
I see movements come and I see movements

00:10:22.520 --> 00:10:27.520
go. People talk about the Word of Faith

00:10:24.560 --> 00:10:29.640
movement, the skinny

00:10:27.520 --> 00:10:31.240
jean fog machine movement. You've got all

00:10:29.640 --> 00:10:34.480
these different movements. I say let's

00:10:31.240 --> 00:10:34.480
just stay filled.

00:10:34.880 --> 00:10:39.240
Let's just stay filled with the Holy

00:10:36.520 --> 00:10:39.240
Ghost.

00:10:39.480 --> 00:10:44.000
The Holy Spirit's always talking. He's

00:10:41.839 --> 00:10:46.320
always imparting. He's always leading.

00:10:44.000 --> 00:10:48.280
He's always guiding.

00:10:46.320 --> 00:10:51.240
There's always new wine and new wineskins.

00:10:48.280 --> 00:10:53.000
The moment you go before Him

00:10:51.240 --> 00:10:56.040
and you spend time with Him, He will

00:10:53.000 --> 00:10:57.600
fill your cup to overflow.

00:10:56.040 --> 00:11:01.280
But there's a lot of you who don't even

00:10:57.600 --> 00:11:04.520
have anything in your cup anymore.

00:11:01.280 --> 00:11:06.720
Your cup has become empty.

00:11:04.520 --> 00:11:09.920
And God is calling a new generation to

00:11:06.720 --> 00:11:11.760
rise up and tell the

00:11:09.920 --> 00:11:14.640
people that the soon-coming of the Lord

00:11:11.760 --> 00:11:14.640
is at hand.

00:11:14.839 --> 00:11:22.080
I get so tired of the labels and

00:11:17.960 --> 00:11:22.080
the charismatic flakiness—pretending

00:11:22.280 --> 00:11:26.680
you have it when you lost it

00:11:24.760 --> 00:11:29.480
a long time ago.

00:11:26.680 --> 00:11:31.560
Go back to where you lost it

00:11:29.480 --> 00:11:33.600
and find out what you did to grieve the

00:11:31.560 --> 00:11:35.599
Holy Spirit in your life and say, 'Lord,

00:11:33.600 --> 00:11:38.000
I repent,'and get right with Him and

00:11:35.600 --> 00:11:40.640
get your cup filled up again. All you

00:11:38.000 --> 00:11:44.000
have to do is surrender all,

00:11:40.640 --> 00:11:46.880
and He'll fill your cup to overflow.

00:11:44.000 --> 00:11:49.520
But I see these visions of

00:11:46.880 --> 00:11:53.840
these demonic people who are

00:11:49.520 --> 00:11:55.880
so obsessed and possessed with demonic spirits

00:11:53.840 --> 00:11:58.880
trying to kill, steal, and destroy

00:11:55.880 --> 00:12:00.200
because they see fruit in what they do.

00:11:58.880 --> 00:12:01.439
But the body of Christ is just like,

00:12:00.200 --> 00:12:04.000
'Well, we'll go out and we'll have a

00:12:01.440 --> 00:12:05.680
little five-minute sermon

00:12:04.000 --> 00:12:07.200
with a little bit of

00:12:05.680 --> 00:12:09.439
something for 30

00:12:07.200 --> 00:12:10.840
minutes or whatever. We're in and out.

00:12:09.440 --> 00:12:12.040
We'll make sure we take up the

00:12:12.040 --> 00:12:14.760
offering.'We've

00:12:14.760 --> 00:12:18.080
got to stop playing church like

00:12:16.360 --> 00:12:20.400
this.

00:12:18.080 --> 00:12:22.120
As I'm seeing in Colombia, the Lord said this man is

00:12:20.400 --> 00:12:24.360
in danger.

00:12:22.120 --> 00:12:25.760
And I thought, 'Dear God, Lord, you're

00:12:24.360 --> 00:12:28.000
giving me another assignment for another man.'And

00:12:25.760 --> 00:12:28.960
so then I found out he watches

00:12:28.000 --> 00:12:31.840
me.

00:12:28.960 --> 00:12:33.640
That's why I'm talking this way.

00:12:31.840 --> 00:12:35.760
I found out he watches my channel and he

00:12:33.640 --> 00:12:38.000
knows that I pray.

00:12:35.760 --> 00:12:40.240
I was told by a pastor,

00:12:38.000 --> 00:12:42.960
because I told him what I saw today,

00:12:40.240 --> 00:12:44.920
and he said, 'He watches you.

00:12:42.960 --> 00:12:46.400
He knows who you are.'So

00:12:44.920 --> 00:12:48.439
the reason I'm bringing this up, sir,

00:12:46.400 --> 00:12:49.640
is because I know you watch.

00:12:48.440 --> 00:12:50.880
I'm saying it in front of thousands of

00:12:49.640 --> 00:12:52.160
people,

00:12:50.880 --> 00:12:54.160
but I'm trying to tell you there's an

00:12:52.160 --> 00:12:56.360
assignment against your life. There's an

00:12:54.160 --> 00:12:58.319
assignment against your friends. But

